WEBVTT

00:00:13.766 --> 00:00:15.768
Je, kuna nambari tunayoweza kuwapigia wazazi wako?

00:00:15.851 --> 00:00:17.937
Nywele zako ziko wapi? Je, una saratani?

00:00:18.020 --> 00:00:19.230
Ulikimbia?

00:00:19.313 --> 00:00:21.232
-Je, uko katika shida fulani? -Je, hiyo ni damu?

00:00:22.024 --> 00:00:24.109
-Acha! Unamtisha! -Ananitisha!

00:00:24.193 --> 00:00:25.402
Naamini yeye ni kiziwi.

00:00:27.488 --> 00:00:28.572
Sio kiziwi.

00:00:28.656 --> 00:00:31.951
Sawa, hiyo inatosha, sawa? Anaogopa na baridi tu.

00:00:38.582 --> 00:00:40.417
Hapa, hizi ni safi. Sawa?

00:00:51.136 --> 00:00:52.388
- Hapana, hapana, hapana!

00:00:52.471 --> 00:00:54.098
Ee Mungu wangu. Ee Mungu wangu.

00:00:54.181 --> 00:00:57.434
- Unaona pale? - Hiyo ni bafuni.

00:00:57.518 --> 00:00:59.520
Faragha. Unaelewa?

00:01:14.743 --> 00:01:15.911
Hutaki ifungwe?

00:01:17.746 --> 00:01:18.747
Hapana.

00:01:18.831 --> 00:01:20.916
Loo, ili uweze kuzungumza.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.210
Sawa, sawa...

00:01:23.294 --> 00:01:27.298
Um, vipi kuhusu sisi tuendelee tu...

00:01:29.550 --> 00:01:31.135
kama hivi tu.

00:01:31.635 --> 00:01:34.346
-Je, hiyo ni bora zaidi? -Ndiyo.

00:01:39.977 --> 00:01:42.104
- Hii ni ya kiakili. - Angalau anaweza kuzungumza.

00:01:42.187 --> 00:01:45.065
Alisema "hapana" na "ndio." Dada yako wa miaka mitatu anasema zaidi.

00:01:45.149 --> 00:01:46.859
Alijaribu kuwa uchi.

00:01:46.942 --> 00:01:48.569
Kuna kitu kibaya sana kwake.

00:01:48.652 --> 00:01:52.156
-Kama, ni makosa kichwani. -Alikwenda tu kama...

00:01:52.239 --> 00:01:53.699
Naamini alitoroka kutoka Pennhurst.

00:01:53.782 --> 00:01:56.410
-Kutoka wapi? -Nyumba ya watu wasio na ujuzi katika Kaunti ya Kerley.

00:01:56.493 --> 00:01:58.120
-Una familia nyingi hapo? -Niume.

00:01:58.203 --> 00:02:00.205
Kwa uzito, fikiria kuhusu hilo.

00:02:00.289 --> 00:02:03.334
Hilo lingeelezea jinsi alivyonyoa nywele zake na kwa nini ana kichaa sana.

00:02:03.417 --> 00:02:04.543
Kwa nini alienda kama...

00:02:04.627 --> 00:02:07.421
Yeye ni mtoro ndio hoja kuu. Huenda ni mtu mwenye akili timamu.

00:02:07.504 --> 00:02:09.506
- Kama Michael Myers. - Hasa!

00:02:09.590 --> 00:02:11.175
Hatupaswi kamwe kumleta hapa.

00:02:11.258 --> 00:02:12.593
Kwa hivyo ulitaka tu kumwacha nje katika dhoruba hiyo?

00:02:12.676 --> 00:02:15.429
Ndiyo! Tulitoka nje kumtafuta Will, si tatizo lingine.

00:02:15.512 --> 00:02:17.222
-Nadhani tunapaswa kumwambia mama yako. -Naunga mkono hilo.

00:02:17.306 --> 00:02:19.266
-Nani sasa ni mwendawazimu? -Je, huyo ni mwendawazimu vipi?

00:02:19.350 --> 00:02:21.935
Kwa sababu, hatukupaswa kuwa nje usiku wa leo, unakumbuka?

00:02:22.019 --> 00:02:24.355
-Kwa hivyo? -Kwa hivyo nikimwambia mama yangu

00:02:24.438 --> 00:02:26.273
na anamwambia mama yako na mama yako...

00:02:26.357 --> 00:02:28.609
-Ah, jamani. -Nyumba zetu zinakuwa Alcatraz.

00:02:28.692 --> 00:02:31.278
Hasa. Hatutampata Will kamwe.

00:02:33.030 --> 00:02:35.574
Sawa, huu ndio mpango. Analala hapa usiku wa leo.

00:02:35.658 --> 00:02:37.785
-Unamruhusu msichana -- -Sikiliza tu!

00:02:37.868 --> 00:02:39.828
Asubuhi, anazunguka-zunguka nyumbani kwangu kisiri,

00:02:39.912 --> 00:02:41.955
anaenda kwenye mlango wa mbele na kupiga kengele ya mlango wangu.

00:02:42.039 --> 00:02:43.832
Mama yangu atajibu na kujua hasa la kufanya.

00:02:43.916 --> 00:02:46.168
Atamrudisha Pennhurst au popote anapotokea.

00:02:46.251 --> 00:02:47.378
Tutakuwa wazi kabisa.

00:02:47.461 --> 00:02:49.254
Na kesho usiku, tutarudi nje.

00:02:49.338 --> 00:02:51.715
Na wakati huu, tunampata Will.

00:02:56.345 --> 00:02:58.347
Haya basi. Huu ni mfuko wangu wa kulalia.

00:02:58.430 --> 00:03:00.724
Unafikiri kweli ana akili timamu?

00:03:00.808 --> 00:03:02.393
Sitaki aingie nyumbani kwangu.

00:03:06.814 --> 00:03:08.440
Akili.

00:03:10.609 --> 00:03:12.778
Halo, um, sijawahi kuuliza jina lako.

00:03:20.244 --> 00:03:21.495
Je, hiyo ni kweli?

00:03:24.331 --> 00:03:28.585
Samahani, sijawahi kuona mtoto mwenye tatoo hapo awali.

00:03:29.420 --> 00:03:31.213
Inamaanisha nini? Kumi na moja?

00:03:34.550 --> 00:03:35.676
Hilo ndilo jina lako?

00:03:37.803 --> 00:03:39.847
Kumi na moja. Sawa.

00:03:39.930 --> 00:03:43.267
Um, sawa, jina langu ni Mike. Kifupi cha Michael.

00:03:43.350 --> 00:03:46.562
Labda tunaweza kukuita "El." Kifupi cha Kumi na Moja.

00:03:50.607 --> 00:03:52.025
Um, sawa, sawa.

00:03:52.943 --> 00:03:54.194
'Usiku, El.'

00:03:56.447 --> 00:03:57.740
'Usiku, Mike.'

00:05:52.145 --> 00:05:55.816
Sawa, Mama. Kiamsha kinywa kiko tayari.

00:05:55.899 --> 00:05:58.694
-Nini? Hapana, kuwa mwangalifu na bango. -Ndiyo, sawa. Sawa.

00:05:58.777 --> 00:06:00.654
-Siwezi kula. -Nahitaji tu ule, Mama.

00:06:00.737 --> 00:06:04.157
Sikiliza. Sikiliza, sehemu ya Xerox inafunguliwa ndani ya dakika 30 hivi.

00:06:04.241 --> 00:06:05.659
-Ndiyo. -Na sitaki uende peke yako...

00:06:05.742 --> 00:06:06.827
Hapana, najua. Nilikuambia, nimeelewa.

00:06:06.910 --> 00:06:09.329
...kwa hivyo nitamtaka Karen akupeleke, kwa sababu ninapaswa kuwa hapa.

00:06:09.413 --> 00:06:11.790
-Sawa. -Tunahitaji kutengeneza, nakala 200, 300?

00:06:11.873 --> 00:06:13.000
-Nakala moja ni kiasi gani? -Ndiyo, sawa.

00:06:13.083 --> 00:06:14.167
-Sawa, Mama. Mama. -Senti kumi?

00:06:14.251 --> 00:06:16.878
- Kama sisi... Senti kumi-- - Mama. Mama. Mama!

00:06:16.962 --> 00:06:19.214
Huwezi kuwa hivi, sawa?

00:06:19.298 --> 00:06:21.717
-Samahani. Samahani. -Hapana, ni sawa.

00:06:24.303 --> 00:06:27.598
Tumekuwa tukisubiri kwa saa sita.

00:06:27.681 --> 00:06:29.391
Najua. Nilikuja haraka iwezekanavyo.

00:06:29.474 --> 00:06:31.059
Saa sita.

00:06:31.143 --> 00:06:33.270
Kuna imani kidogo hapa, sawa?

00:06:33.353 --> 00:06:36.315
Tumekuwa tukitafuta usiku kucha. Tulienda hadi Cartersville.

00:06:36.398 --> 00:06:38.066
-Na? -Hakuna.

00:06:38.150 --> 00:06:39.568
Mungu.

00:06:42.237 --> 00:06:43.655
Flo anasema umepigiwa simu?

00:06:43.739 --> 00:06:45.907
Loo, ndio.

00:06:53.206 --> 00:06:54.833
Dhoruba ilichoma vizuri sana.

00:06:54.916 --> 00:06:57.336
-Dhoruba? -Nini kingine?

00:06:57.419 --> 00:07:00.339
Unasema kwamba hilo si jambo la ajabu?

00:07:00.422 --> 00:07:02.090
Hapana, ni ajabu.

00:07:02.174 --> 00:07:04.676
Je, tunaweza, kama, kufuatilia ni nani aliyepiga simu? Wasiliana na--

00:07:04.760 --> 00:07:06.762
Hapana, haifanyi kazi hivyo.

00:07:06.845 --> 00:07:08.597
Sasa, uh, una uhakika ilikuwa Will?

00:07:08.680 --> 00:07:10.349
Kwa sababu Flo alisema umesikia pumzi kidogo tu.

00:07:10.432 --> 00:07:13.477
Hapana. Alikuwa yeye. Alikuwa Will.

00:07:14.478 --> 00:07:18.523
Na aliogopa. Na kisha kitu fulani--

00:07:18.607 --> 00:07:21.443
Huenda ilikuwa ni simu ya utani tu. Ilikuwa ni mtu anayejaribu kukutisha.

00:07:21.526 --> 00:07:23.278
-Nani angefanya hivyo? -Naam, jambo hili limekuwa likionyeshwa kwenye TV.

00:07:23.362 --> 00:07:26.531
Inaleta wazimu wote, unajua. Mawazo ya uwongo, miito ya utani, uh...

00:07:26.615 --> 00:07:29.618
Hapana, Hopper, haikuwa mzaha. Ilikuwa yeye.

00:07:29.701 --> 00:07:32.329
-Joyce. -Haya, vipi kuhusu uaminifu mdogo hapa?

00:07:33.330 --> 00:07:35.624
Unafikiri mimi... ninabuni hili?

00:07:35.707 --> 00:07:37.167
Sisemi kwamba unaitunga.

00:07:37.250 --> 00:07:39.711
Ninachosema ni kwamba ni wakati wa hisia kwako.

00:07:39.795 --> 00:07:43.090
Na unafikiri sijui jinsi mwanangu anavyopumua?

00:07:43.173 --> 00:07:44.800
Je, hungejua ya binti yako mwenyewe?

00:07:58.689 --> 00:08:01.858
-Umesikia kutoka kwa Lonnie bado? -Hapana.

00:08:02.442 --> 00:08:04.319
Imekuwa muda mrefu wa kutosha. Ninampeleka nje ya kliniki.

00:08:04.403 --> 00:08:06.071
Loo, njoo!

00:08:06.154 --> 00:08:08.240
Unapoteza muda wako.

00:08:10.200 --> 00:08:11.952
Habari, Hopper.

00:08:12.035 --> 00:08:14.204
Mrukaji.

00:08:14.287 --> 00:08:15.539
Niache niende.

00:08:17.165 --> 00:08:18.959
-Samahani? -Kwa Lonnie's.

00:08:19.042 --> 00:08:21.920
Unajua, ikiwa Will yuko pale, inamaanisha alikimbia.

00:08:22.004 --> 00:08:24.423
Na akionana na polisi, atafikiri yuko matatani.

00:08:24.506 --> 00:08:26.216
Ata... Atajificha.

00:08:26.299 --> 00:08:28.010
-Unajua, ni mzuri wa kujificha. -Ndiyo?

00:08:29.177 --> 00:08:31.430
Naam, polisi ni wazuri katika kutafuta. Sawa?

00:08:31.513 --> 00:08:33.181
Kaa hapa na mama yako.

00:08:34.391 --> 00:08:35.475
Anakuhitaji.

00:08:54.202 --> 00:08:56.830
Punguza mwendo, Mike. Hilo ni jambo la kuchukiza.

00:08:58.290 --> 00:09:00.167
Ulisoma sana jana usiku?

00:09:00.917 --> 00:09:02.836
Ndiyo, kwa kweli, nilifanya hivyo.

00:09:02.919 --> 00:09:05.297
Ulikuwa na kipimo gani tena? Anatomia ya binadamu?

00:09:07.340 --> 00:09:09.092
Hei, nini kinaendelea?

00:09:10.385 --> 00:09:11.595
Hakuna kitu.

00:09:23.023 --> 00:09:24.399
Halo, umepata supercomm yangu.

00:09:24.483 --> 00:09:25.650
Vizuri sana, sivyo?

00:09:26.318 --> 00:09:27.611
Ninazungumza na marafiki zangu nayo.

00:09:27.694 --> 00:09:29.571
Zaidi ni Lucas, kwa sababu anaishi karibu sana.

00:09:29.654 --> 00:09:30.739
Ishara ni dhaifu sana.

00:09:34.951 --> 00:09:36.119
Nimekupatia kifungua kinywa.

00:09:38.705 --> 00:09:40.665
Kwa hivyo sikiliza, hii itasikika kama ya ajabu kidogo,

00:09:40.749 --> 00:09:42.084
lakini nahitaji tu uende huko nje.

00:09:42.167 --> 00:09:44.294
Kisha nenda kwenye mlango wa mbele na upige kengele ya mlango.

00:09:44.377 --> 00:09:47.923
Mama yangu atajibu na utamwambia kwamba umepotea na kwamba unahitaji msaada.

00:09:48.006 --> 00:09:52.135
Lakini chochote utakachofanya, huwezi kumwambia kuhusu jana usiku au kwamba unanijua.

00:09:52.219 --> 00:09:53.220
Unaelewa?

00:09:54.346 --> 00:09:55.722
Kwa kweli, si jambo kubwa.

00:09:55.806 --> 00:09:57.933
Tutajifanya tu kukutana tena.

00:09:58.934 --> 00:10:01.603
Na mama yangu, atajua ni nani wa kumpigia simu.

00:10:04.064 --> 00:10:05.107
Hapana.

00:10:06.399 --> 00:10:07.526
Hapana?

00:10:08.360 --> 00:10:09.361
Hapana.

00:10:10.362 --> 00:10:13.782
Hapana... hutaki mama yangu apate msaada?

00:10:18.578 --> 00:10:21.123
Uko kwenye shida, sivyo?

00:10:24.960 --> 00:10:26.002
WHO...

00:10:27.462 --> 00:10:29.131
Una shida na nani?

00:10:31.883 --> 00:10:33.426
Mbaya.

00:10:33.510 --> 00:10:34.594
Mbaya?

00:10:35.595 --> 00:10:36.763
Watu wabaya?

00:10:40.433 --> 00:10:42.477
Wanataka kukudhuru?

00:10:42.561 --> 00:10:43.979
Watu wabaya?

00:10:53.738 --> 00:10:55.407
Unaelewa?

00:10:56.491 --> 00:10:58.994
Michael, uko wapi? Tutachelewa.

00:10:59.077 --> 00:11:00.787
- Twende! - Sawa, nitarudi.

00:11:00.871 --> 00:11:02.622
Kaa hapa tu, sawa? Kaa hapa.

00:11:09.963 --> 00:11:11.381
Hii ilikuwa lini?

00:11:11.464 --> 00:11:13.091
Jana usiku. Chini ya maili mbili kutoka hapa.

00:11:13.174 --> 00:11:14.968
-Na mvulana? -Bado haipo.

00:11:15.719 --> 00:11:18.763
Ilikuwa mwanangu. Najua.

00:11:18.847 --> 00:11:21.141
Na mimi... nilisikia kitu kingine.

00:11:21.224 --> 00:11:22.601
Kitu kingine?

00:11:23.810 --> 00:11:27.314
Ilikuwa kama, uh, aina fulani ya mnyama.

00:11:27.397 --> 00:11:30.901
Sijui. Tafadhali mwambie Hop afanye haraka.

00:11:30.984 --> 00:11:33.904
Will! Will Byers!

00:11:34.779 --> 00:11:36.656
Will Byers!

00:11:39.200 --> 00:11:41.494
- Mapenzi! - Mapenzi!

00:11:41.578 --> 00:11:44.331
Hujambo! Kitu chochote?

00:11:45.290 --> 00:11:46.333
Wewe?

00:11:47.292 --> 00:11:49.544
Hapana, hakuna kingine ila simu iliyokufa.

00:11:49.628 --> 00:11:50.629
Joyce?

00:11:50.712 --> 00:11:53.465
Karibu hatua moja kutoka kuanguka kutoka ukingoni.

00:11:53.548 --> 00:11:55.967
Amekuwa hatua chache kwa muda sasa, sivyo?

00:11:56.051 --> 00:11:57.802
Mtoto amepotea, jamani.

00:11:57.886 --> 00:11:59.179
Onyesha darasa dogo.

00:12:00.180 --> 00:12:02.682
Sawa. Haya, twende!

00:12:02.766 --> 00:12:05.018
Tuna mengi ya kufunika.

00:12:05.101 --> 00:12:07.520
Mkuu na yeye, wamewahi kugombana hapo awali, sivyo?

00:12:10.065 --> 00:12:11.733
Je, utapenda!

00:12:11.816 --> 00:12:13.276
Hiyo ni "ndio" au walifanya hivyo...

00:12:14.319 --> 00:12:16.404
-Will! -Will!

00:12:23.954 --> 00:12:27.374
"Chembe za alfa zinapopita kwenye karatasi ya dhahabu, huwa..."

00:12:27.457 --> 00:12:30.001
-Nafasi isiyo na watu. -"Molekuli inayoweza--"

00:12:30.085 --> 00:12:31.169
- Haya! - Sijui,

00:12:31.252 --> 00:12:32.545
Nadhani umesoma vya kutosha, Nance.

00:12:32.629 --> 00:12:34.673
- Steve-- - Ninakuambia, unajua, umeelewa hili.

00:12:34.756 --> 00:12:37.092
Usijali. Sasa, tuendelee kwenye mambo muhimu zaidi.

00:12:37.175 --> 00:12:40.136
Baba yangu ameondoka mjini kwenye mkutano na mama yangu ameenda naye,

00:12:40.220 --> 00:12:42.639
-kwa sababu, unajua, hamwamini. -Simu nzuri.

00:12:42.722 --> 00:12:43.723
Kwa hivyo uko ndani?

00:12:43.807 --> 00:12:45.225
Kwa ajili ya nini?

00:12:45.308 --> 00:12:47.060
Hakuna wazazi? Nyumba kubwa?

00:12:47.727 --> 00:12:48.853
Sherehe?

00:12:48.937 --> 00:12:50.855
- Ding, ding, ding!

00:12:50.981 --> 00:12:52.399
Ni Jumanne.

00:12:52.482 --> 00:12:53.942
Ni Jumanne! Ee Mungu wangu.

00:12:54.025 --> 00:12:55.360
--Njoo.

00:12:55.443 --> 00:12:57.195
Itakuwa jambo la busara. Itakuwa sisi tu.

00:12:57.278 --> 00:12:59.656
Unasemaje? Uko ndani au uko nje?

00:12:59.739 --> 00:13:03.576
-Um... -Ee Mungu. Tazama.

00:13:04.577 --> 00:13:06.287
Ee Mungu, hilo linasikitisha.

00:13:08.498 --> 00:13:11.751
-Je, tuseme kitu? -Sidhani kama anaongea.

00:13:11.835 --> 00:13:13.586
Unataka kuweka dau kiasi gani kwamba alimuua?

00:13:13.670 --> 00:13:14.921
Nyamaza.

00:13:22.220 --> 00:13:23.722
Habari.

00:13:23.805 --> 00:13:25.390
Loo, hujambo.

00:13:25.473 --> 00:13:26.641
Mimi tu...

00:13:27.809 --> 00:13:31.104
Nilitaka kusema, unajua, um...

00:13:31.187 --> 00:13:33.106
Samahani kwa kila kitu.

00:13:38.528 --> 00:13:40.822
Kila mtu anakufikiria.

00:13:42.949 --> 00:13:45.618
-Inasikitisha. -Ndiyo.

00:13:49.122 --> 00:13:50.373
Nina uhakika yuko sawa.

00:13:50.457 --> 00:13:52.125
Ni mtoto mwerevu.

00:13:55.045 --> 00:13:56.921
Lazima niende. Mtihani wa Kemia.

00:13:57.005 --> 00:13:58.006
Ndiyo.

00:13:58.089 --> 00:13:59.549
-Bahati nzuri. -Asante.

00:14:04.345 --> 00:14:06.890
Umakinifu, walimu na wanafunzi.

00:14:06.973 --> 00:14:10.435
Saa 8:00 usiku wa leo, kutakuwa na mkutano kwenye uwanja wa mpira wa miguu

00:14:10.518 --> 00:14:12.854
kwa kumuunga mkono Will Byers na familia yake.

00:14:12.937 --> 00:14:15.065
Wote wanahimizwa kuhudhuria.

00:14:15.148 --> 00:14:19.319
Usajili wa kujitolea kwa ajili ya watu wanaotafuta bado unapatikana ofisini.

00:14:25.492 --> 00:14:26.701
Loo, hii ni ajabu.

00:14:27.160 --> 00:14:30.163
-Hajawahi kuchelewa hivi. -Nakuambia, mpango wake wa kijinga ulishindwa.

00:14:30.246 --> 00:14:31.498
Nilidhani umependa mpango wake.

00:14:31.581 --> 00:14:33.917
Ndiyo, lakini ni wazi ilikuwa ni ujinga, la sivyo angekuwa hapa.

00:14:34.000 --> 00:14:35.960
Ikiwa mama yake angegundua msichana angelala usiku kucha--

00:14:36.044 --> 00:14:37.545
Yuko katika hali mbaya sana hivi sasa.

00:14:37.629 --> 00:14:40.298
Vipi kama angelala uchi?

00:14:40.382 --> 00:14:42.300
Mungu wangu, hakufanya hivyo.

00:14:42.384 --> 00:14:44.594
Loo, kama Bi. Wheeler atawaambia wazazi wangu...

00:14:44.677 --> 00:14:47.555
-Hapana. Mike hangetupinga kamwe. -Sijui.

00:14:47.639 --> 00:14:50.850
Kinachojalisha ni kwamba, baada ya shule, mtu huyo atarudi kwenye pipa la takataka,

00:14:50.934 --> 00:14:54.062
na tunaweza kuzingatia kile ambacho ni muhimu sana, kumpata Will.

00:15:10.203 --> 00:15:11.413
Unataka kinywaji chochote?

00:15:11.496 --> 00:15:14.165
Tuna OJ, maziwa yaliyopunguzwa mafuta... Nini kingine?

00:15:15.500 --> 00:15:16.876
Um, tuna...

00:15:18.795 --> 00:15:20.547
Loo, hiki ni sebule yangu.

00:15:20.630 --> 00:15:22.173
Zaidi ni kwa ajili ya kutazama TV tu.

00:15:22.257 --> 00:15:24.801
Nzuri, sivyo? Ni inchi 22.

00:15:24.884 --> 00:15:26.970
Hiyo, kama, ni kubwa mara kumi kuliko ya Dustin.

00:15:38.440 --> 00:15:40.692
-Mzuri. -Nadhani.

00:15:40.775 --> 00:15:42.193
Huyo ni dada yangu Nancy.

00:15:42.277 --> 00:15:43.903
Na huyo ni mtoto Holly.

00:15:43.987 --> 00:15:45.363
Na hao ni wazazi wangu.

00:15:46.030 --> 00:15:47.157
Wazazi wako wakoje?

00:15:47.782 --> 00:15:49.200
Je, wanaishi karibu?

00:15:51.619 --> 00:15:53.204
Huyo ndiye La-Z-Boy wetu.

00:15:54.914 --> 00:15:56.166
Ni mahali ambapo baba yangu analala.

00:15:56.249 --> 00:15:58.960
Unaweza kujaribu ikiwa unataka.

00:15:59.627 --> 00:16:00.628
Ndiyo.

00:16:01.963 --> 00:16:02.964
Ni furaha.

00:16:06.593 --> 00:16:08.428
Niamini tu, sawa?

00:16:14.267 --> 00:16:15.935
Unaona? Furaha, sivyo?

00:16:17.812 --> 00:16:18.813
Sasa jaribu.

00:16:53.473 --> 00:16:56.226
♪ Mpenzi, lazima unijulishe ♪

00:16:57.769 --> 00:17:01.481
♪ Je, nibaki au niende? ♪

00:17:01.564 --> 00:17:03.191
-Unaipenda? -Ndiyo, ni nzuri.

00:17:03.274 --> 00:17:04.943
Sawa, unaweza kuweka mchanganyiko huo ukitaka.

00:17:05.026 --> 00:17:06.152
-Kweli? -Ndiyo, kweli.

00:17:06.236 --> 00:17:07.820
Mambo yote bora yapo hapo.

00:17:07.904 --> 00:17:10.823
Kitengo cha Joy, Bowie, Televisheni, The Smiths...

00:17:10.907 --> 00:17:12.617
Itabadilisha maisha yako kabisa.

00:17:12.700 --> 00:17:14.369
Ndiyo, kabisa.

00:17:14.452 --> 00:17:16.538
Uko wapi jamani, Lonnie?

00:17:16.621 --> 00:17:18.081
Sitaki kuisikia. Sitaki kuisikia.

00:17:22.835 --> 00:17:26.923
Hii ni ujinga! Nimechoka sana na visingizio vyako.

00:17:27.006 --> 00:17:29.801
♪ Siku moja ni sawa na inayofuata ni nyeusi ♪

00:17:29.884 --> 00:17:31.386
--Haji, sivyo?

00:17:33.096 --> 00:17:34.472
Je, unapenda hata besiboli?

00:17:35.598 --> 00:17:37.809
Hapana, lakini... Sijui.

00:17:37.892 --> 00:17:39.894
-Ni furaha kwenda naye wakati mwingine. -Njoo.

00:17:39.978 --> 00:17:42.730
Je, amewahi kufanya jambo lolote na wewe ambalo unalipenda kweli?

00:17:42.814 --> 00:17:44.566
Unajua, kama ukumbi wa michezo au kitu kama hicho?

00:17:45.358 --> 00:17:48.069
-Sijui. -Hapana, sawa? Hajajua.

00:17:48.152 --> 00:17:49.988
Anajaribu kukulazimisha kupenda mambo ya kawaida.

00:17:50.071 --> 00:17:53.116
Na hupaswi kupenda vitu kwa sababu watu wanakuambia unapaswa kupenda.

00:17:53.199 --> 00:17:54.492
Sawa?

00:17:55.285 --> 00:17:56.995
Hasa si yeye.

00:17:58.871 --> 00:18:01.249
Lakini unapenda The Clash? Kweli?

00:18:01.332 --> 00:18:03.459
Kwa kweli. Bila shaka.

00:18:05.837 --> 00:18:08.590
♪ Je, niipoeze au niipulize? ♪

00:18:10.216 --> 00:18:14.596
♪ Kwa hivyo lazima unijulishe ♪

00:18:14.679 --> 00:18:16.556
♪ Je, nibaki au niende? ♪

00:18:40.788 --> 00:18:43.207
Joyce, sikukutarajia leo.

00:18:43.291 --> 00:18:46.419
- Nilimleta Jeffrey ili aje aandike. - Sipo hapa kufanya kazi.

00:18:46.502 --> 00:18:47.920
Mimi...

00:18:48.004 --> 00:18:50.131
Dhoruba jana usiku, mimi...

00:18:50.757 --> 00:18:52.925
Nahitaji simu mpya.

00:18:54.135 --> 00:18:57.555
Sawa, hiyo inaonekana kama $22.56.

00:18:57.639 --> 00:18:59.432
Uh, ndio, unajua, uh...

00:18:59.515 --> 00:19:01.809
Nilimpa Jonathan pesa zangu zote kwa ajili ya...

00:19:01.893 --> 00:19:03.686
kwa nakala za mabango.

00:19:04.687 --> 00:19:07.148
Uh, nahitaji mapema.

00:19:08.066 --> 00:19:09.567
Ndiyo, sawa, bila shaka.

00:19:09.651 --> 00:19:11.235
- Bila shaka. - Asante.

00:19:16.157 --> 00:19:18.660
Ndiyo, uh, nilikuwa nafikiria, wiki mbili?

00:19:20.912 --> 00:19:22.163
Moja...

00:19:23.956 --> 00:19:27.293
Ndiyo, naelewa, lakini, unajua, lazima nimlipe Jeffrey kwa ajili ya kufunika--

00:19:27.377 --> 00:19:28.378
Donald.

00:19:28.461 --> 00:19:31.673
Nimekuwa hapa kwa miaka kumi, sivyo?

00:19:31.756 --> 00:19:35.718
Je, nimewahi kupiga simu nikiwa mgonjwa au kukosa zamu mara moja?

00:19:35.802 --> 00:19:39.180
Nimefanya kazi, uh, Sikukuu ya Krismasi na Shukrani.

00:19:40.640 --> 00:19:42.684
Sijui kijana wangu yuko wapi.

00:19:42.767 --> 00:19:43.976
Ameenda.

00:19:44.060 --> 00:19:48.106
Sijui kama nitamuona tena, kama ameumia...

00:19:49.857 --> 00:19:51.192
Mimi, uh...

00:19:52.735 --> 00:19:56.447
Ninahitaji simu hii na wiki mbili mapema.

00:20:00.076 --> 00:20:01.828
Na kundi la Ngamia.

00:20:12.171 --> 00:20:14.132
- Sote tuko wazi. - Nakili hilo.

00:21:11.481 --> 00:21:13.107
Ajabu.

00:21:16.486 --> 00:21:18.946
Uko tayari? Ni nini kinachokujua uko tayari?

00:21:19.030 --> 00:21:20.323
Jina lake ni Yoda.

00:21:20.406 --> 00:21:23.534
Anaweza kutumia Nguvu kuhamisha mambo kwa akili yake, kama hivi.

00:21:23.618 --> 00:21:24.952
Duuuh!

00:21:26.704 --> 00:21:28.414
Loo, huyu ni dinosaur wangu, Rory.

00:21:28.498 --> 00:21:30.333
Tazama, ana kipaza sauti mdomoni mwake ili aweze kunguruma.

00:21:39.091 --> 00:21:41.385
Loo, haya yote ni mataji yangu ya maonyesho ya sayansi.

00:21:41.469 --> 00:21:43.805
Tulipata nafasi ya kwanza kila mwaka.

00:21:43.888 --> 00:21:46.599
Isipokuwa mwaka jana tuliposhika nafasi ya tatu.

00:21:46.682 --> 00:21:48.768
Bw. Clarke alisema ilikuwa ya kisiasa kabisa.

00:22:08.746 --> 00:22:09.872
Unamjua Will?

00:22:10.915 --> 00:22:15.044
Ulimwona? Jana usiku? Akiwa njiani?

00:22:21.551 --> 00:22:22.718
Lazima tuondoke.

00:22:26.264 --> 00:22:28.307
Nilinunua pizza na makaroni.

00:22:28.391 --> 00:22:29.934
- Sawa. - Sawa.

00:22:33.437 --> 00:22:35.565
Ted? Je, huyo ni wewe?

00:22:35.648 --> 00:22:36.857
Mimi tu, Mama!

00:22:36.941 --> 00:22:39.610
-Mike? Unafanya nini nyumbani? -Sekunde moja!

00:22:44.031 --> 00:22:45.950
Hapa ndani. Nitarudi mara moja, sawa?

00:22:46.033 --> 00:22:48.744
Tafadhali, lazima uingie, la sivyo mama yangu, atakupata.

00:22:48.828 --> 00:22:50.788
Unaelewa?

00:22:50.871 --> 00:22:52.456
Sitamwambia kukuhusu. Naahidi.

00:22:52.540 --> 00:22:53.916
Ahadi?

00:22:54.000 --> 00:22:56.002
Inamaanisha kitu ambacho huwezi kukivunja.

00:22:56.085 --> 00:22:58.004
- Je, umewahi. - Michael?

00:22:58.629 --> 00:22:59.672
Tafadhali?

00:23:17.440 --> 00:23:18.733
Piga!

00:23:22.945 --> 00:23:24.280
Baba!

00:23:25.573 --> 00:23:26.866
Baba!

00:23:26.949 --> 00:23:28.284
Hapana!

00:23:29.201 --> 00:23:30.328
Baba!

00:23:30.411 --> 00:23:32.747
Hapana! Hapana! Hapana!

00:23:37.543 --> 00:23:38.586
Baba!

00:23:38.669 --> 00:23:40.338
- Baba!

00:23:40.421 --> 00:23:41.839
Baba!

00:23:41.922 --> 00:23:44.008
Baba!

00:23:44.091 --> 00:23:45.259
Baba!

00:23:48.846 --> 00:23:49.889
Bodi.

00:23:59.482 --> 00:24:01.901
Mimi tu... Sijisikii vizuri.

00:24:01.984 --> 00:24:04.654
Niliamka na kichwa changu, kiliuma sana,

00:24:04.737 --> 00:24:06.947
na koo langu lilikuwa na mikwaruzo yote, na nilitaka kukuambia,

00:24:07.031 --> 00:24:08.407
lakini mara ya mwisho nilikuambia nilikuwa mgonjwa

00:24:08.491 --> 00:24:10.409
-umenifanya niende shuleni hata hivyo, na-- -Michael.

00:24:10.493 --> 00:24:13.329
-Ndiyo? -Sikukasirikia.

00:24:13.412 --> 00:24:16.707
-Hapana? -Hapana, bila shaka sivyo.

00:24:19.043 --> 00:24:21.962
Haya yote ambayo yamekuwa yakiendelea na Will,

00:24:22.046 --> 00:24:24.173
Siwezi kufikiria jinsi ilivyokuwa kwako.

00:24:25.508 --> 00:24:26.967
Mimi tu...

00:24:27.510 --> 00:24:29.512
Nataka uhisi kama unaweza kuzungumza nami.

00:24:29.595 --> 00:24:33.349
Sitaki kamwe uhisi kama unapaswa kunificha chochote.

00:24:33.432 --> 00:24:35.559
Niko hapa kwa ajili yako. Sawa?

00:24:38.145 --> 00:24:39.313
Je, kuna mtu mwingine hapa?

00:24:41.023 --> 00:24:42.024
Hapana.

00:24:44.151 --> 00:24:45.528
Kumi na moja?

00:24:45.611 --> 00:24:47.196
Je, kila kitu kiko sawa?

00:24:47.279 --> 00:24:48.322
Yeye?

00:24:52.743 --> 00:24:54.704
- Mike. - Je, kila kitu kiko sawa?

00:24:57.665 --> 00:24:59.125
Una uhakika?

00:25:00.418 --> 00:25:01.794
Ahadi.

00:25:37.830 --> 00:25:41.333
- Will Byers! - Will!

00:25:43.544 --> 00:25:44.962
Ole, ole. Makini, makini.

00:25:45.045 --> 00:25:47.256
Nakuhitaji uishi kwa siku chache zijazo, angalau.

00:25:47.339 --> 00:25:49.592
Loo, jamani, ningeweza kuishi hivyo.

00:25:50.760 --> 00:25:52.803
Nini? George Burness aliruka.

00:25:52.887 --> 00:25:55.222
Na alikuwa amelewa kama skunk. Alifanya hivyo kwa dau la $10.

00:25:55.306 --> 00:25:56.307
George ni mwongo.

00:25:56.390 --> 00:25:59.268
Unafanya kuruka kutoka urefu huu, maji hayo yanageuka kuwa saruji.

00:25:59.351 --> 00:26:01.854
Inakupiga kama tani ya matofali. Vunja kila mfupa mwilini mwako.

00:26:04.940 --> 00:26:06.150
Sasa.

00:26:06.233 --> 00:26:08.027
Mkuu, unakili?

00:26:09.612 --> 00:26:11.113
Ndiyo, Flo, zungumza nami.

00:26:11.197 --> 00:26:13.949
Habari, Mkuu, tumepokea simu kutoka Benny's.

00:26:14.033 --> 00:26:15.868
Nadhani unahitaji kufika huko mara moja.

00:26:38.808 --> 00:26:40.309
Ugh, Yesu!

00:26:46.482 --> 00:26:47.608
Kujiua?

00:26:49.068 --> 00:26:50.569
Mmm-hmm.

00:26:50.653 --> 00:26:52.738
Mtoto aliyepotea, kujiua...

00:26:52.822 --> 00:26:55.533
Lazima ujisikie kama polisi wa jiji kubwa tena, sivyo, Mkuu?

00:26:57.243 --> 00:26:59.995
Naam, nilikuwa nikishughulika zaidi na wageni wakati huo.

00:27:02.456 --> 00:27:04.250
Benny alikuwa rafiki yangu.

00:27:41.036 --> 00:27:42.329
Habari?

00:27:43.622 --> 00:27:44.832
Ndiyo.

00:27:47.960 --> 00:27:50.254
-Naweza kukusaidia? -Ndiyo, Lonnie yuko hapa?

00:27:50.337 --> 00:27:52.339
-Ndiyo, yuko nje. Unataka nini? -Kuangalia huku na huko.

00:27:52.423 --> 00:27:54.925
-Hei, unafikiri unafanya nini? Hei! -Nitaharakisha.

00:27:55.009 --> 00:27:56.343
Hujambo, Will?

00:27:56.427 --> 00:27:57.803
Je, utapenda!

00:27:57.887 --> 00:27:59.972
Je, uko hapa? Je, uko hapa!

00:28:04.894 --> 00:28:06.103
Ondoka!

00:28:07.271 --> 00:28:08.856
Laana, umekuwa na nguvu zaidi.

00:28:08.939 --> 00:28:11.066
Je, kuna mtu tafadhali aeleze kinachoendelea?

00:28:12.026 --> 00:28:15.321
Jonathan, Cynthia. Cynthia, huyu ni Jonathan.

00:28:15.404 --> 00:28:16.405
Mzee wangu.

00:28:18.490 --> 00:28:21.368
-Njoo hapa. -Niondokee, jamani.

00:28:34.548 --> 00:28:36.842
-Je, umerukwa na akili? -Nisikilize tu.

00:28:36.926 --> 00:28:38.719
-Umerukwa na akili! -Anajua kuhusu Will.

00:28:38.802 --> 00:28:40.512
Unamaanisha anajua nini kuhusu Will?

00:28:41.639 --> 00:28:44.683
Alimwonyesha, kwenye picha yake. Alijua alikuwa amepotea. Niliweza kujua.

00:28:44.767 --> 00:28:46.644
- Unaweza kujua? - Hebu fikiria kuhusu hilo.

00:28:46.727 --> 00:28:48.938
Unafikiri kweli ilikuwa bahati mbaya kwamba tulimkuta Mirkwood,

00:28:49.021 --> 00:28:50.648
mahali pale pale ambapo Will alitoweka?

00:28:50.731 --> 00:28:53.025
-Hilo ni jambo la ajabu. -Na alisema watu wabaya wanamtafuta.

00:28:53.108 --> 00:28:56.403
Nadhani labda watu hawa wabaya ndio wale wale waliomchukua Will.

00:28:56.487 --> 00:28:59.865
-Nadhani anajua kilichompata. -Kwa nini basi hatuambii?

00:29:02.034 --> 00:29:04.078
Unajua yuko wapi?

00:29:04.161 --> 00:29:05.162
Unajua Will yuko wapi?

00:29:05.246 --> 00:29:07.581
-Acha, unamtisha! -Anapaswa kuogopa!

00:29:07.665 --> 00:29:10.542
Kama unajua alipo, tuambie!

00:29:11.877 --> 00:29:14.421
Huyu ni mjinga. Tunapaswa kumpeleka kwa mama yako.

00:29:14.505 --> 00:29:16.924
Hapana! Kumi na mmoja walisema kumwambia mtu mzima yeyote kutatuweka hatarini.

00:29:17.007 --> 00:29:19.426
-Hatari ya aina gani? -Jina lake ni kumi na moja?

00:29:19.510 --> 00:29:22.012
-El kwa ufupi. -Mike, ni hatari ya aina gani?

00:29:22.096 --> 00:29:23.722
Hatari hatari.

00:29:29.561 --> 00:29:31.480
Hapana, hapana, hapana!

00:29:31.563 --> 00:29:34.316
Tunarudi kwenye mpango A. Tunamwambia mama yako.

00:29:45.911 --> 00:29:46.996
Hapana.

00:29:53.210 --> 00:29:55.921
Mtazame mrembo huyu. Ningepaswa kumuona nilipompata.

00:29:56.005 --> 00:29:57.881
Ilinichukua mwaka mmoja, lakini karibu imekamilika.

00:29:58.882 --> 00:30:01.760
Kweli? Unataka kunichunguza pia?

00:30:02.428 --> 00:30:04.263
Nilikuambia kitu kile kile kama nilivyowaambia polisi hao,

00:30:04.346 --> 00:30:05.931
hayupo hapa na hajawahi kuwapo.

00:30:06.015 --> 00:30:09.018
-Basi kwa nini hukumpigia simu Mama tena? -Sijui, mimi tu...

00:30:09.101 --> 00:30:11.603
Nilidhani amesahau tu mahali alipokuwa.

00:30:11.687 --> 00:30:13.230
Unajua, alikuwa amepotea au kitu kama hicho.

00:30:14.273 --> 00:30:16.567
Mvulana huyo hakuwahi kuwa mzuri sana katika kujitunza.

00:30:16.650 --> 00:30:19.778
Huu si utani, sawa? Kuna watu wanaotafuta, waandishi wa habari...

00:30:19.862 --> 00:30:21.196
Hopper bado si mkuu, sivyo?

00:30:23.324 --> 00:30:26.410
Mwambie mama yako kwamba lazima akutoe kwenye shimo hilo la kuzimu.

00:30:26.493 --> 00:30:28.454
Njoo hapa mjini.

00:30:28.537 --> 00:30:30.164
Watu ni halisi zaidi hapa, unajua?

00:30:31.540 --> 00:30:32.958
Na kisha ningeweza kukuona zaidi.

00:30:35.127 --> 00:30:37.588
-Vipi, unafikiri sitaki kukuona? -Najua hutaki.

00:30:37.671 --> 00:30:39.715
Unaona, huyo ni mama yako anayezungumza hapo hapo.

00:30:40.966 --> 00:30:42.092
Anajua hata uko hapa?

00:30:43.135 --> 00:30:44.136
Loo, vizuri sana.

00:30:44.219 --> 00:30:46.930
Kwa hivyo mtoto mmoja anapotea, mwingine anakimbia sana?

00:30:47.014 --> 00:30:48.807
Uzazi mzuri sana hapo hapo.

00:30:48.891 --> 00:30:52.644
Tazama, ninachosema ni kwamba, labda mimi si mkorofi, sawa?

00:30:57.358 --> 00:30:59.026
Ikiwa umesahau jinsi anavyoonekana.

00:31:02.613 --> 00:31:04.365
Yeye ni mrembo kidogo, hmm?

00:31:04.448 --> 00:31:06.492
Labda nitakubadilisha kwa mwanamitindo mdogo?

00:31:08.952 --> 00:31:10.496
Haina maana yoyote, Mkuu.

00:31:14.041 --> 00:31:15.459
Wewe, uh, unaona chochote...

00:31:16.502 --> 00:31:17.878
ajabu kumhusu wiki chache zilizopita?

00:31:17.961 --> 00:31:21.215
Hapana, tunajiandaa kwenda kuvua samaki kwenye Etowah Jumapili ijayo.

00:31:21.298 --> 00:31:23.425
Namaanisha, alikuwa akiitarajia. Ninajua hilo.

00:31:23.509 --> 00:31:25.719
Ana maadui wowote unaoweza kuwajua?

00:31:25.803 --> 00:31:27.888
Namaanisha, watu ambao huenda wasimtaki karibu naye?

00:31:27.971 --> 00:31:30.974
Wapenzi wa zamani hawakumpenda sana. Hiyo ni hakika, lakini...

00:31:31.975 --> 00:31:33.519
Sasa.

00:31:33.602 --> 00:31:37.356
-Mara ya mwisho ulimwona lini? -Jana. Chakula cha mchana, kama kawaida.

00:31:37.439 --> 00:31:39.691
-Wewe na wavulana tu? -Ndiyo.

00:31:39.775 --> 00:31:41.860
Mimi na Henry na...

00:31:43.153 --> 00:31:45.697
Naam, kulikuwa na huyu, uh, mtoto huyu.

00:31:46.698 --> 00:31:47.825
Hakuna mtoto aliyefanya hivi.

00:31:48.784 --> 00:31:49.827
Kijana?

00:31:51.245 --> 00:31:52.704
Unazungumzia nini?

00:31:52.788 --> 00:31:57.709
Ndiyo. Wakati wa chakula cha mchana, uh, kulikuwa na mvulana huyu ambaye, uh...

00:31:57.793 --> 00:32:00.546
Namaanisha, alikuwa akijaribu kuiba chakula kutoka jikoni mwa Benny.

00:32:00.629 --> 00:32:02.005
Je, unaweza kufikiria hilo?

00:32:04.967 --> 00:32:06.009
Mtoto huyu...

00:32:07.636 --> 00:32:08.762
Alikuwa na sura gani?

00:32:09.930 --> 00:32:13.225
Naam, alikuwa na urefu wa juu wa yeah. Unajua, mdogo kama.

00:32:13.308 --> 00:32:15.686
Hata hivyo, sikumtazama vizuri. Alikuwa amerudi jikoni.

00:32:15.769 --> 00:32:17.229
Anaonekana hivi?

00:32:18.021 --> 00:32:20.941
Loo, hapana, hiyo ni... Huyo ni mtoto wa Lonnie aliyepotea.

00:32:21.024 --> 00:32:23.068
Hapana. Huyu alikuwa mtoto tofauti.

00:32:23.152 --> 00:32:24.611
Huyu alikuwa na nywele fupi sana.

00:32:24.695 --> 00:32:26.780
Namaanisha, ilikuwa ikisikika karibu hadi kwenye kichwa cha kichwa.

00:32:26.864 --> 00:32:29.491
Naam, hebu... Unajua, hebu tusahau kuhusu kukata nywele.

00:32:29.575 --> 00:32:32.661
Namaanisha, kama mtoto huyu angekuwa na msisimko...

00:32:32.744 --> 00:32:34.121
Je, inaweza kuwa mtoto wa Lonnie?

00:32:34.872 --> 00:32:37.166
Naam, mimi... sikumtazama vizuri.

00:32:39.168 --> 00:32:41.128
Hata hivyo, kuhusu urefu unaofaa.

00:32:41.211 --> 00:32:42.880
Namaanisha, ingeweza kuwa hivyo.

00:32:43.964 --> 00:32:45.632
Ndiyo, hiyo ni...

00:32:45.716 --> 00:32:46.717
Ingeweza kuwa.

00:32:50.220 --> 00:32:52.931
Kwa sababu sitaki kwenda peke yangu.

00:32:53.015 --> 00:32:56.185
Barb... Barb, si sayansi ya roketi.

00:32:56.268 --> 00:32:59.646
Utawaambia wazazi wako kwamba utakaa nyumbani kwangu baadaye.

00:32:59.730 --> 00:33:02.608
Hapana, waambie tunajifunza...

00:33:02.691 --> 00:33:04.401
Nancy! Chakula cha jioni!

00:33:04.485 --> 00:33:06.195
Inakuja!

00:33:06.278 --> 00:33:08.947
Tazama, lazima niondoke. Nitakuona baada ya saa moja.

00:33:18.665 --> 00:33:20.292
Kuna tatizo lolote na mkate wa nyama?

00:33:21.168 --> 00:33:24.213
Loo, hapana, nilikula sandwichi mbili za bologna kwa chakula cha mchana.

00:33:26.006 --> 00:33:27.007
Sijui ni kwa nini.

00:33:27.090 --> 00:33:28.967
Mimi pia.

00:33:30.177 --> 00:33:32.513
-Ni kitamu, Mama. -Asante, mpenzi.

00:33:33.347 --> 00:33:34.973
Kwa hivyo, kuna hii...

00:33:35.057 --> 00:33:37.559
jambo la mkutano maalum usiku wa leo...

00:33:37.643 --> 00:33:39.937
kwa Will katika uwanja wa shule.

00:33:40.020 --> 00:33:41.021
Barb anaendesha gari.

00:33:41.104 --> 00:33:43.273
Kwa nini nasikia tu kuhusu hili?

00:33:44.149 --> 00:33:45.192
Nilidhani unajua.

00:33:45.275 --> 00:33:48.362
Nilikuambia, sitaki utoke gizani hadi Will apatikane.

00:33:48.445 --> 00:33:51.782
Najua, najua, lakini itakuwa ajabu sana kama sipo.

00:33:51.865 --> 00:33:53.909
Namaanisha, kila mtu anaenda.

00:33:57.162 --> 00:33:59.081
Tu... nitarudi ifikapo saa 10:00.

00:34:00.499 --> 00:34:01.667
Kwa nini usiwachukue wavulana pia?

00:34:01.750 --> 00:34:02.960
-Hapana! -Mmm-mmm.

00:34:04.628 --> 00:34:06.713
Hufikirii unapaswa kuwa hapo? Kwa ajili ya Will?

00:34:10.759 --> 00:34:13.011
Samahani. Mkazo.

00:34:16.890 --> 00:34:19.142
--Loo...

00:34:19.226 --> 00:34:20.435
Ni sawa, Holly.

00:34:20.519 --> 00:34:22.354
-Ni kelele kubwa tu. -Nzuri.

00:34:24.064 --> 00:34:26.358
--Je, utapenda!

00:34:28.443 --> 00:34:31.655
Bora utoke nje, rafiki. Will, uko wapi?

00:34:41.999 --> 00:34:44.876
Unadhani Earl alimuona Will kweli?

00:34:44.960 --> 00:34:47.921
Namaanisha, anafanya nini na kichwa kilichonyolewa?

00:34:48.005 --> 00:34:49.590
Na kuiba chakula kutoka kwa Benny?

00:34:49.673 --> 00:34:52.342
Tutakuambia nini, tutakapompata, tutauliza.

00:34:52.426 --> 00:34:54.052
Siwezi kuuliza maswali ya maiti.

00:34:54.136 --> 00:34:55.929
--Subiri!

00:34:56.013 --> 00:34:57.472
Una kitu?

00:35:00.642 --> 00:35:02.769
- Haya, una nini? - Sina uhakika.

00:35:02.853 --> 00:35:04.771
Labda hakuna kitu.

00:35:04.855 --> 00:35:06.773
Nimeipata hii. Ndani yake.

00:35:11.486 --> 00:35:13.655
Hakuna njia yoyote mtoto anaweza kutambaa hapo.

00:35:14.698 --> 00:35:16.408
Sijui...

00:35:16.491 --> 00:35:17.868
mtu mwenye hofu ya kutosha anaweza.

00:35:17.951 --> 00:35:20.329
Ndugu yake alisema alikuwa hodari wa kujificha.

00:35:56.448 --> 00:35:57.449
Yeye?

00:36:03.246 --> 00:36:06.208
Hakuna watu wazima. Sisi tu na mkate wa nyama.

00:36:09.670 --> 00:36:12.798
Usijali. Hawatamwambia mtu yeyote kukuhusu.

00:36:12.881 --> 00:36:15.300
Wanaahidi. Sivyo?

00:36:15.384 --> 00:36:17.928
Hatungekukasirisha kamwe kama tungejua una nguvu kubwa.

00:36:19.262 --> 00:36:20.305
Oh!

00:36:20.389 --> 00:36:25.018
Kile ambacho Dustin anajaribu kusema ni kwamba walikuwa wameogopa tu... mapema.

00:36:25.102 --> 00:36:26.144
Hiyo ndiyo yote.

00:36:26.228 --> 00:36:28.146
Tulitaka tu kumpata rafiki yetu.

00:36:28.730 --> 00:36:29.773
"Rafiki"?

00:36:29.856 --> 00:36:32.734
Ndiyo, rafiki. Je, utakubali?

00:36:32.818 --> 00:36:36.113
"Rafiki" ni nini?

00:36:36.196 --> 00:36:37.614
Je, yeye ni mzito?

00:36:40.283 --> 00:36:41.702
Um, rafiki--

00:36:41.785 --> 00:36:43.537
Ni mtu ambaye ungemfanyia chochote.

00:36:43.620 --> 00:36:46.748
Unawakopesha vitu vyako vya kupendeza, kama vile vitabu vya katuni na kadi za biashara.

00:36:46.832 --> 00:36:48.125
Na hawavunji ahadi kamwe.

00:36:48.208 --> 00:36:50.127
-Hasa wakati kuna mate. -Mate?

00:36:50.210 --> 00:36:53.964
- Kuapa kwa mate kunamaanisha... - huvunji neno lako kamwe.

00:36:54.047 --> 00:36:55.465
Ni kifungo.

00:36:55.549 --> 00:36:59.219
Hilo ni muhimu sana, kwa sababu marafiki...

00:36:59.302 --> 00:37:01.555
wanaambiana mambo.

00:37:01.638 --> 00:37:03.390
Mambo ambayo wazazi hawayajui.

00:37:10.230 --> 00:37:12.274
- Barbara, simama. - Nini?

00:37:12.357 --> 00:37:13.650
Vuta!

00:37:16.361 --> 00:37:18.238
Tunafanya nini hapa?

00:37:18.321 --> 00:37:19.906
Nyumba yake iko umbali wa vitalu vitatu.

00:37:19.990 --> 00:37:21.450
Hatuwezi kuegesha magari kwenye njia ya kuingilia.

00:37:21.533 --> 00:37:22.576
Je, uko makini?

00:37:22.659 --> 00:37:23.785
Ndiyo, majirani wanaweza kuona.

00:37:23.869 --> 00:37:26.580
Huu ni ujinga sana. Nitakuacha tu.

00:37:26.663 --> 00:37:28.498
Tulia, Barb. Njoo.

00:37:28.582 --> 00:37:31.126
Uliahidi kwamba utaenda. Unakuja.

00:37:31.209 --> 00:37:32.461
Tutakuwa na wakati mzuri.

00:37:32.544 --> 00:37:34.087
Anataka tu kuingia kwenye suruali yako.

00:37:34.171 --> 00:37:35.797
Hapana, hafanyi hivyo.

00:37:35.881 --> 00:37:38.175
Nance... kwa uzito.

00:37:39.301 --> 00:37:41.344
Alikualika nyumbani kwake.

00:37:41.970 --> 00:37:43.346
Wazazi wake hawapo nyumbani.

00:37:44.014 --> 00:37:45.682
Haya, wewe si mjinga hivi.

00:37:45.766 --> 00:37:47.768
Tommy H. na Carol watakuwepo.

00:37:47.851 --> 00:37:50.937
Tommy na Carol wamekuwa wakifanya ngono tangu, kama darasa la saba.

00:37:51.938 --> 00:37:53.899
Huenda ikawa tu, kama vile, sherehe kubwa ya ngono.

00:37:53.982 --> 00:37:56.943
-Kwa kiasi kikubwa. -Niko makini!

00:37:57.027 --> 00:37:58.320
Sawa, sawa...

00:37:59.321 --> 00:38:02.574
Unaweza kuwa, kama mlezi wangu. Sawa?

00:38:02.657 --> 00:38:05.118
Hakikisha silewi na kufanya jambo lolote la kijinga.

00:38:05.202 --> 00:38:06.203
Ugh.

00:38:09.539 --> 00:38:10.749
Je, hiyo ni sidiria mpya?

00:38:12.417 --> 00:38:13.543
Hapana.

00:38:26.306 --> 00:38:27.974
Pole, baridi.

00:38:28.892 --> 00:38:30.268
Nina baridi.

00:38:35.357 --> 00:38:36.733
Habari zenu wanawake.

00:39:08.849 --> 00:39:10.308
Unafanya nini?

00:39:11.309 --> 00:39:12.811
Inaganda.

00:39:18.692 --> 00:39:20.068
Umewahi kuhisi umelaaniwa?

00:39:23.530 --> 00:39:26.575
Unajua, mtu wa mwisho kupotea hapa alikuwa ndani, uh...

00:39:28.368 --> 00:39:29.953
majira ya joto ya '23.

00:39:31.621 --> 00:39:33.915
Kujiua kwa mwisho kulikuwa ni msimu wa vuli wa '61.

00:39:39.212 --> 00:39:41.673
Mtu wa mwisho aliganda hadi kufa lini?

00:39:45.176 --> 00:39:47.387
Haya, rudi ndani.

00:39:47.470 --> 00:39:49.472
Nipashe moto. Tu...

00:39:52.100 --> 00:39:53.685
Nipe dakika moja tu hapa.

00:40:20.378 --> 00:40:22.130
Yule mtu wa ajabu anafanya nini?

00:40:28.178 --> 00:40:29.220
Yeye?

00:40:42.817 --> 00:40:43.902
Will.

00:40:44.569 --> 00:40:45.570
Nguvu Kuu.

00:40:52.702 --> 00:40:55.622
Ulimwona? Kwenye Mirkwood?

00:40:57.040 --> 00:40:58.249
Unajua yuko wapi?

00:41:14.140 --> 00:41:15.850
Sielewi.

00:41:16.768 --> 00:41:17.936
Kujificha.

00:41:18.061 --> 00:41:19.688
Will anajificha?

00:41:24.442 --> 00:41:26.027
Kutoka kwa watu wabaya?

00:41:28.947 --> 00:41:30.615
Kisha kutoka kwa nani?

00:42:34.262 --> 00:42:35.805
Uko wapi?

00:43:04.876 --> 00:43:07.170
--Moja! Mbili!

00:43:07.253 --> 00:43:09.923
- Tatu! - Acha, Tommy, hapana! Usifanye hivyo!

00:43:10.006 --> 00:43:12.675
-- Wewe ni mjinga sana, Tommy.

00:43:27.899 --> 00:43:29.609
Je, hilo linapaswa kunivutia?

00:43:30.401 --> 00:43:33.488
-Wewe sivyo? -Wewe ni msemo wa kawaida, unatambua hilo?

00:43:33.571 --> 00:43:34.614
Wewe ni msemo wa kawaida.

00:43:34.697 --> 00:43:37.117
Vipi kuhusu... alama zako na mazoezi yako ya bendi?

00:43:37.200 --> 00:43:38.618
Siko kwenye bendi sana.

00:43:38.701 --> 00:43:41.621
Sawa, msichana wa sherehe. Kwa nini usituonyeshe tu jinsi inavyofanyika?

00:43:41.704 --> 00:43:42.705
Sawa.

00:43:49.838 --> 00:43:51.756
-Lazima utoboe shimo dogo ndani -- -Nimeelewa.

00:43:51.840 --> 00:43:54.050
Ndiyo, yeye ni mwerevu, wewe mpuuzi!

00:43:58.680 --> 00:44:00.807
Chuki, chuki, chuki.

00:44:00.890 --> 00:44:02.350
Chug. Chug. Chug. Chug.

00:44:14.904 --> 00:44:16.156
Barb, unataka kujaribu?

00:44:16.990 --> 00:44:18.533
Nini? Hapana.

00:44:18.616 --> 00:44:19.868
Hapana, sitaki. Asante.

00:44:19.951 --> 00:44:21.077
- Njoo. - Ndiyo...

00:44:21.161 --> 00:44:22.495
- Njoo. Ndiyo. - Nance, sitaki.

00:44:22.579 --> 00:44:24.289
-Ni furaha! Ipe tu -- -Nance...

00:44:24.372 --> 00:44:26.040
Tu... Jaribu tu.

00:44:28.251 --> 00:44:29.294
Sawa.

00:44:34.883 --> 00:44:36.009
Kwa hivyo wewe tu...

00:44:40.722 --> 00:44:42.765
- Gnarly. - Uko sawa?

00:44:42.849 --> 00:44:44.309
- Ndiyo. - Barb, unatokwa na damu.

00:44:44.392 --> 00:44:46.352
Niko sawa. Bafu yako iko wapi?

00:44:46.436 --> 00:44:49.022
Loo, ni... Ni, uh, chini kupita jikoni, upande wa kushoto.

00:44:49.105 --> 00:44:50.690
Sawa. Asante.

00:44:53.651 --> 00:44:55.194
Loo!

00:45:04.078 --> 00:45:07.206
Mungu wangu! Nini basi, Tommy?

00:45:07.290 --> 00:45:08.291
Hapana!

00:45:09.918 --> 00:45:11.836
--Huu!

00:45:52.001 --> 00:45:53.044
Habari?

00:45:55.254 --> 00:45:57.840
- Habari.

00:45:57.924 --> 00:45:59.759
Huyu ni nani?

00:46:02.845 --> 00:46:05.098
- Je, nitafanya?

00:46:06.557 --> 00:46:09.310
--Will, ni mimi.

00:46:09.394 --> 00:46:11.145
Zungumza nami.

00:46:11.229 --> 00:46:12.605
Niko hapa.

00:46:12.689 --> 00:46:14.565
Niambie tu uko wapi, mpenzi.

00:46:14.649 --> 00:46:16.609
- Naweza kukusikia. Tafadhali.

00:46:17.610 --> 00:46:19.278
- Mama?

00:46:19.362 --> 00:46:20.738
Je, utapenda!

00:46:20.822 --> 00:46:24.450
Ndiyo, ni mimi. Ni mimi.

00:46:24.534 --> 00:46:26.828
Uko wapi? Uko wapi? Zungumza nami tu--

00:46:29.497 --> 00:46:30.540
Loo, hapana, hapana!

00:46:30.623 --> 00:46:31.666
Hapana!

00:46:31.749 --> 00:46:33.251
Hapana!

00:46:33.334 --> 00:46:36.045
Loo, hapana! Hapana, hapana...

00:46:38.923 --> 00:46:40.216
Hapana!

00:46:46.305 --> 00:46:48.182
Hapana!

00:47:04.699 --> 00:47:06.075
Yonathani?

00:47:08.703 --> 00:47:09.704
Nini...

00:47:41.402 --> 00:47:42.445
Je,...

00:47:54.624 --> 00:47:56.209
Je,...

00:47:57.335 --> 00:47:59.003
Will, ni wewe?

00:48:22.276 --> 00:48:23.653
Ee Mungu wangu.

00:48:26.364 --> 00:48:27.949
Ee Mungu...

00:48:30.910 --> 00:48:33.037
Ee Mungu wangu...

00:49:17.248 --> 00:49:19.125
--Ninaganda.

00:49:19.208 --> 00:49:23.504
Hmm... nasikia chumba cha mama yake kina mahali pa moto.

00:49:23.588 --> 00:49:24.839
- Unatania? - Loo, ndio?

00:49:24.922 --> 00:49:27.258
Sawa, unajua, unasafisha shuka.

00:49:27.341 --> 00:49:28.593
-Uko sawa? -Ndiyo.

00:49:28.676 --> 00:49:31.345
Ndiyo? Njoo, tukununulie nguo kavu.

00:49:36.893 --> 00:49:38.186
Nance!

00:49:38.311 --> 00:49:39.604
Nancy.

00:49:40.563 --> 00:49:42.315
Unaenda wapi?

00:49:42.398 --> 00:49:43.441
Hakuna mahali popote.

00:49:43.524 --> 00:49:45.359
Tu ... ghorofani.

00:49:45.443 --> 00:49:47.069
Kubadilisha.

00:49:47.153 --> 00:49:49.906
Nilianguka kwenye bwawa la kuogelea.

00:49:52.658 --> 00:49:54.535
Kwa nini usiendelee na kurudi nyumbani?

00:49:54.619 --> 00:49:56.996
Nita... Nitapata usafiri au kitu kama hicho.

00:49:57.079 --> 00:49:58.456
Nance...

00:49:59.207 --> 00:50:00.917
Barb...

00:50:01.000 --> 00:50:02.585
Niko sawa.

00:50:02.668 --> 00:50:05.087
Huyu si wewe.

00:50:06.214 --> 00:50:07.840
Niko sawa.

00:50:07.924 --> 00:50:11.510
Tu... endelea na uende nyumbani, sawa?

00:50:31.405 --> 00:50:32.657
Asante.

00:50:37.453 --> 00:50:38.996
Moja...

00:50:39.080 --> 00:50:40.706
faragha fulani, labda?

00:50:40.790 --> 00:50:42.291
Loo...

00:50:42.375 --> 00:50:44.001
Ndiyo, sawa. Samahani.

00:50:48.756 --> 00:50:49.799
Steve?

00:51:03.813 --> 00:51:04.981
Laana.

00:51:07.316 --> 00:51:08.567
Nyamaza.